Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}超越無人所及的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(980,993.75)}ものがたり
